fields.job_description: I recently had a surgery on my leg and I cannot exert any effort on it while I rest and recover from it. Since my partner is on the night shift at his work, he also can't take our dog out for her morning walks. My dog is a two years old labrador, and she is very good-tempered.  I would appreicate if someone were able to walk her on the weekday mornings next week.

I urgently need a babysitter because the babyminder I hired is sick and and there is no one else at home to take care of my kid as I need to take my mom to a doctor's appointment at the hospital. My son is twelve years old so the Care Inspectorate in Scotland is required for this job.  This hopefully shouldn't take more than two hours!

My children painted on one of the walls in my house with crayon and I want to apply a fresh coat of paint before the holidays roll around and guests come to visit.  If anyone has experience painting walls, I would really appreciate if you could help me do this. I can provide the paint and I am relatively flexible with when the painting can be done.

Hi there! I would like someone to help my daughter with her math coursework on the weekend. She is a third grade student at the local elementary school if that helps you understand the situation better. Right now they are working on basic arithmetic, including the four operations (+, -, *, and /) and their order in PEMDAS problems. She also started learning about fractions so knowing how to explain that would also be useful. Everyone is encouraged to apply, but applicants with previous experiences in tutoring will be prioritized.

My grandma is a wheelchair user and has other mobility-related disabilities that make it hard for her to do her weekly shopping by herself.  She would like someone who could accompany her to her shopping and help her reach higher shelves and carry her cart. This job would ideally operate on a weekly basis so that she can replenish her stock of food and supplies.

The grass in my front yard has not been trimmed for a long time. The patch is about fifty meters long and ten meters wide. I struggle to control it because I don't have the tools or the energy to maintain it by myself. This job is hard work but can be done within one day.
I have an important job interview on Friday.  I would greatly appreciate it if somebody could loan me a suit (ideally something close to a 2.5R measurement) for the interview before Friday afternoon.

I need someone to help me collect my package from the parcel store because I will be out of town for a week-long trip and this was the only time it could be delivered. All I need you to do is to collect the parcel and hold onto it until next Thursday. We can arrange a preferred way of me getting the package from you privately.

I have a heartburn emergency! It's uncomfortable but not dangerous. It would be amazing it if someone could pick up my order for antacid tablets at the grocery store on the corner of Bedford Place.  Thank you all in advance!

After the thunderstorm, a window in my house shattered. I'm very lost at how to repair the window and what supplies I need to get to do it, so if anyone here can help with the doing that please reach out.
I need a qualified teacher to help my son with his homework. He is a second grade pupil. Main subjects are Mathematics and Science. 2 hours couse on Friday.
